  "notes": "Audit is QUALIFIED - auditors unable to obtain sufficient evidence for $347,950 in tax refund revenues related to the gas station (CRA and Revenu Qu\u00e9bec tax reports not available). Fiscal year is March 31, 2021. Two subsidiaries fully consolidated: Corporation de d\u00e9veloppement \u00e9conomique Wabak Pimadizi and Transport Wabak. One GBE-like entity: Coop\u00e9rative de Solidarit\u00e9 Wabak (accounted for at cost, not equity method, has going concern issues). 48% proportional consolidation of Chalets Modik partnership with SEPAQ. Significant pandemic-related funding in 2021. Large increase in deferred revenue and uninvested surpluses. Debt covenant violations noted on gas station loan reclassified to current. Retirement plan charge was $1,241,385. Province is Quebec (QC)."
